marketing: Shell Gadus S5 V460KP is a specialised wind turbine grease, designed to perform in demanding applications and severe operating conditions. Shell recognises that reliability is paramount, especially considering the logistical, safety and cost considerations for maintenance on installed turbines. Therefore Shell Gadus S5 V460KP is formulated to offer an impressive combination of component protection and long service life, whatever the climate or weather.
